com.inmobi.conduit.utils
Class LocalStreamDataConsistency

java.lang.Object
  com.inmobi.conduit.utils.CompareDataConsistency
      com.inmobi.conduit.utils.LocalStreamDataConsistency

public class LocalStreamDataConsistency
extends CompareDataConsistency

This class is used to check the data consistency between data(data + trash) and streams_local. It takes 3 arguments. 1st one is set of root directories, second argument is set of stream names and 3rd argument is set of collector names. Second and third arguments are optional here.
